bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">π</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≤</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">π</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">by_cases!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">case</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">hn</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cast_zero</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">div_zero</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">positivity</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">case</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">neg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">trans</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">π</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">gcongr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">aesop</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>All grind invocations fail.<br>\nThis is a bit annoying.<br>\nIs there an easy fix?</p>",
