        "content": "<p>The first three work with</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">attribute</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">grind</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cast_lt</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
